data.description: Great ranch home in a small neighborhood in Baldwin. Close to 365/985 & Hwy 441, shopping, & restaurants. Level lot on a quiet neighborhood street. 3 beds & 1.5 baths, Screened back deck overlooks the backyard with two outbuildings. One outbuilding is wired & has electricity. Eat in kitchen, laundry room off the kitchen, pantry, carbon monoxide alarm system. This would be a great starter home or investment property.
